5","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would pray eleven cycles in the night. When dawn arrived, he would pray two brief cycles, then lie on his right side until the caller came to announce the prayer. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6310, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 736 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11562,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/walking-salat-waiting-imam\/","url_meta":{"origin":14050,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Masjid: Reward for walking to prayer, waiting for Imam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe people with the greatest reward are those who walk the furthest, then the next furthest. Those who wait to pray with the Imam have a greater reward than those who pray alone and then sleep.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15320,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/23\/fajr-sit-until-sunrise\/","url_meta":{"origin":14050,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fajr: The Prophet sits after prayer until sunrise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Samurah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would pray the dawn prayer and sit crossed legged in his place until the sun had risen brightly. Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4850 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Nawawi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25901,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/02\/05\/dua-wake-up-in-night\/","url_meta":{"origin":14050,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication to say when waking up in night","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 5, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever wakes up in the night and says, 'There is no God but Allah, alone without any partner. To Him belong the dominion and all praise, and He has power over all things. All praise is due\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14755,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/28\/salat-al-fajr-khayr-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":14050,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Sunan prayer of Fajr better than world","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTwo cycles of prayer\u00a0before the dawn\u00a0prayer are better than the world and everything in it. They are both more beloved to me than the entire world.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 725 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14050","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=14050"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14050\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14050"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=14050"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=14050"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated"